node.text: Life updateeee 🙌🏼 Gotta go for those goals right 😅 Seriously doesn’t feel real so I had to say it out loud. The best part of this all is I get to stay home with my babies. 😩🙏🏻 Words can’t describe how thankful I am for this opportunity, thank you all for being here ❤️

node.text: Beach day!☀️First pic me trying to get a boogie off harpers face ➡️ 2nd pic Harper no thanks I’ll use this to get the endless sand off my toes instead 🥲Since Harper was a newborn she’s had the most sensitive skin. From diaper rashes to heat rashes and everything in between @waterwipesusa are the world’s purest baby wipes containing simply 2 ingredients: 99.9% water and just a drop of fruit extract. We lovee them for both of our little babes! And use them for ourselves as well 😅 Find them at your local @safeway
